headline: LFC welcomes PayPal as club's official digital payments partner
summary: Liverpool FC is proud to welcome PayPal as the club's official digital payments partner in a new global, multi-year deal. This marks PayPal's first-ever collaboration with a Premier League club, further positioning the company as the smarter way to pay for football fans globally.
